\section{Desugaring Surface to Core} \label{sec:desugar}

Figure~\ref{fig:desugaring} summarizes how surface terms |t|
are desugared into verifier expressions |e| via
%
\begin{itemize}
   \item |De t| which recursively \emph{desugars} surface terms |t| into core expressions |e| using the helpers,
   \item |Me i t| which \emph{casts} binders (variables) |i| to the \emph{``type''} $|t|$,
   \item |tlamx fx x' x e_1 e_2| which encodes the proof obligations and representation for functions.
\end{itemize}